headlines.description: — Wins have been so rare at Kansas over the last decade-plus that it wasn't too surprising when students spilled from the stands and rushed the field to celebrate Lance Leipold's first victory as head coach of the Jayhawks.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kansas scores late to beat S. Dakota 17-14 in Leipold debut
